Welcome to South Florida 🏝☀️ my name is Dennis and I joined Turo because I’m passionate in making travel very simple and seamless. I figured I can put my own spin to it and make a few people happy 😊.

I want to change the way we rent cars, and offer free items to make your life easier. Who travels with a car charger, umbrella, phone mount, etc. 

Rental agencies charge for every little thing and the items you need for safety (phone mount, car charger, umbrella) you have to pay for…   I just want you to be worry free and safe while renting my cars. 

Enjoy and see you at the end of your trip 🚗👋🏿

About Me:
I am dedicated to providing excellent service and ensuring a seamless and enjoyable experience for all our clients. My commitment to responsibility and trustworthiness is rooted in my strong work ethic, attention to detail, and a passion for delivering top-notch service.

Travel Experiences:
I have had the privilege of traveling to various parts of the world, which has given me a profound appreciation for the beauty of different cultures and landscapes. Some of my favorite travel experiences include hiking in the Swiss Alps, exploring the historical streets of Kyoto, and enjoying the vibrant culture of Marrakech. These experiences have not only broadened my horizons but have also taught me the value of excellent transportation and how it can enhance the travel experience.

Hobbies:
In my free time, I enjoy a range of hobbies that keep me engaged and motivated. I'm an avid photographer, capturing the essence of my travel experiences and showcasing the beauty of the world through my lens. Additionally, I have a passion for classic cars, which has driven my involvement in luxury car rental services. These hobbies have allowed me to connect with people who share similar interests and experiences.

Dream Car:
My dream car is the classic and timeless Rolls-Royce Phantom. Its elegance, craftsmanship, and iconic design make it a symbol of luxury and sophistication. I believe that luxury cars are not just vehicles but pieces of art that can elevate any experience, whether it's a special occasion or a luxurious road trip.

Driving Experience:
I take pride in my extensive driving experience, which includes safe and responsible handling of luxury vehicles. As someone who values the importance of safety and professionalism, I ensure that all cars provided by Lesly Luxury Car Rental are meticulously maintained and ready for a safe and enjoyable journey.

Always rent from a licensed rental agency and not from a private person just trying to get their monthly payment covered. Rental agencies maintain and service their fleet better and more often than private owners, and can offer many benefits a private owner cannot, such as the ability to switch vehicles should any issues arise while on your rental. Along with better  maintenance and customer service, most rental companies are incorporated , licensed by both their city and county and have a commercial general liability insurance policy, whereas a private owner likely does not. A rental company is almost always more concerned and attentive to your complete satisfaction as their livelihood, families, and continued success depends on it!

We do absolutely everything possible to provide our clients with a white glove, stress free car rental experience. With peace of mind that the vehicle will be cleaned, sanitized, full of gas, and on time. Communication is very easy, and we are reachable 24 hours a day. * This Car Can NOT be use in any Racing activity, or event. * NO BurnOuts, or Wreckless Driving *You may be subjected to paying parking fee when booking outside of Miami, FL. 

------ RE-FUELING ------ 

Premium Gas Only Please :-) Don't have time to re-fuel the vehicle when you return it? No problem, I'll take care of it. It will be a $10 charge plus the fuel 

------ JUST A FEW CONDITIONS ------ 

(1) Absolutely NO SMOKING (of anything), this includes marijuana. If the vehicles smells of any kind of smoke or marijuana, you will be fully responsible for all costs associated with having the vehicle decontaminated ($150+). 

(2) NO PETS ! Any pet hair found in vehicles may incur additional cleaning fees. 

(3) Turo App Required. For all of our bookings, we do require that you have access to the Turo app on a smartphone during your rental. This will be needed for communication as well as Trip Photos. 

(4) If you need any additional time during your rental please send me a message as there will be a full day charge for the added time surpassing 24h of reservation. You may also extend your rental prior to end time for a much better rate. 

(5) The vehicle will be fully cleaned upon delivery. If the vehicle is returned excessively dirty there will be a cleaning charge. Thank you and we hope to earn your business!
